title: Bobby's Brain Doctor Results + Morgan Wallen On His Recent Arrest + Amy Gets Podcast Hate
itunes:title: Bobby's Brain Doctor Results + Morgan Wallen On His Recent Arrest + Amy Gets Podcast Hate
description:
Bobby shares an update on his trip to the brain doctor. He may be having brain seizures again. Morgan Wallen talks to us about his recent arrest, his new friendship with Kid Rock and songs he’s written for other artists. Plus, Amy took time to read the one star reviews of her '4 Things With Amy Brown' podcast and shares her thoughts on the feedback.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
